al, precise, fast and satisfying approach.</div> </div>  <div>&nbsp;</div></p> 							</div>', '<p id=\"why_join_us\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"><div style=\"text-align:justify\">Our company is a multinational leading company in financial industry. We have a dynamic corporate culture and friendly working environment. We provide an opportunity for you to grow and develop a career. Join us to unleash your potential and be a part of our amazing team!</div></p>', '<img class=\"img-company-logo\" id=\"img_company_logo_2\" src=\"https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/4348/images/logo/4348_logo_0_7705205.jpg\" alt=\"Lowongan PT Mitsui Leasing Capital Indonesia\">', 'Akuntansi Umum/Pembiayaan', ' &#62; Akuntansi &amp; Laporan Keuangan', 'Perbankan / Pelayanan Keuangan ', 'Jakarta Raya ', 'PT Mitsui Leasing Capital Indonesia ', 'Ditayangkan: 14-October-2019 ', ' 							  							  Tutup pada 13-November-2019', '2019-11-13', '2019-10-14', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/human-resources-coordinator-3093111?fr=J&searchRequestToken=82d2cbdb-de83-412c-a3c8-87e4e52593f3&sectionRank=2', 'Jl. M.H. Thamrin Kav 57, Plaza Bank Index lantai 11, Jakarta 10350', 'Human-Resources-Coordinator', 'jabodetabek', 'active'),
