 approval of the Financial Services Authority (OJK), and Operating lease and/or fee based activity with the provision that it does not violate the rules and regulations in the financial services sector.</div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\">From year on year, Mitsui Leasing performance has increased both in total revenue and net income. Mitsui Leasing asset also increased over time. Quite convincing business development of Mitsui Leasing can be seen on the annual report profile.</div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\">In line with the rapid development and progress of the company, as well as the widening of territory area for servicing the Customers, Mitsui Leasing has opened several branches in Jakarta : Warung Buncit, Mangga Dua, Pondok Indah, Central Park, Kelapa Gading and branches in various cities out side Jakarta such as : Serpong, Bekasi, Medan, Semarang, Surabaya, Bandung, Denpasar, Yogyakarta, Balikpapan and Palembang.</div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\">Pursuant to the Company&rsquo;s vision to be a professional and reliable automotive finance company, in doing its business development Mitsui Leasing has a mission and a commitment to provide services and automotive financial solutions timely, accurate and creative to the customers and business partners, by developing the best services system with the technology development &quot;on - line system&quot; and &quot;one day service&quot;.</div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\">Mitsui Leasing has its customers from various level and classes, both companies and individuals. In order to provide the best services and to fulfil the customers need, the Customer Care of Mitsui Leasing always continually handle the customers problems with&nbsp; a professional, precise, fast and satisfying approach.</div> </div>  <div>&nbsp;</div></p> 							</div>', '<p id=\"why_join_us\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"><div style=\"text-a