(159, 'Fraud Investigation and Dispute Services Consultant-PT Ernst &amp; Young Indonesia ', '<div class=\"unselectable wrap-text\" id=\"job_description\"> <div>  <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Join Fraud Investigation &amp; Dispute Services within Assurance and you will help clients work through complex issues of fraud, regulatory compliance and business disputes. You will be part of a multidisciplinary, culturally aligned team that works with clients and their legal advisors.</div>  </div>    <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>    <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>    <div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Job Description</strong></div>    <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>    <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Successful&nbsp;applicant will help clients&nbsp;and the Fraud Investigation &amp; Dispute Services (FIDS) team in identifying potential fraud, incompliance, and other anomalies. The role includes performing data acquisition, digital data review, forensic data analytics, cyber-breach investigation, and working closely with the FIDS team to perform different analysis and strategies required for the engagements.</div>    <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>    <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>    <div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Requirements:</strong></div>    <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>    <ul>  	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Possesses a Bachelor&rsquo;s degree in <strong>Accounting&nbsp;</strong>or <strong>Computer Science/Information Systems</strong> who has high interest in Accounting&nbsp;from&nbsp;a reputable&nbsp;institution;&nbsp;an advanced degree will be&nbsp;a&nbsp;bonus</li>  	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Working&nbsp;experiences in relevant IT services and Consultancy industry will be a great advantage; however, fresh&nbsp;graduates are welcome to apply</li>  	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">High enthusiasm in IT security, digital forensic, data analytics, or cyber area; ability to code&nbsp;and involved in RDBMS projects will be an advantage</li>  	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Excellent&nbsp;skills in both written and verbal Bahasa Indonesia and&nbsp;English</li>  	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Strong analytical thinking, problem solving&nbsp;skills, presentation&nbsp;and communication skills</li>  	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Execution focused and proven ability to get things&nbsp;done</li>  	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Has knowledge and understanding in financial accounting terms and model will be an advantage</li>  </ul>    <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>    <div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Your Client Responsibilities</strong></div>    <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>    <ul>  	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Perform day to day FIDS/FTDS related activities</li>  	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Able to deliver result on the assigned tasks in timely manner</li>  	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Report to the superior regarding issues and risk found during&nbsp;the fieldwork</li>  	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Adhere to EY methodologies, tools and technology</li>  	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Keen to learn new things to improve both&nbsp;technical and&nbsp;soft&nbsp;skill</li>  	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Build and maintain client relationships at all levels</li>  	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Stay informed of general business/economic developments and understand their impact to the client</li>  </ul>    <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>    <div>  <div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Your People Responsibilities</strong></div>    <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>    <ul>  	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Coach, counsel and provide support for staff on all engagements</li>  	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Contribute to performance feedback&nbsp;for team member</li>  	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Contribute&nbsp;to people-related initiatives including recruiting,&nbsp;retaining&nbsp;and training professionals</li>  	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Understand and follow workplace policies and procedures</li>  	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Demonstrate our fundamental values : professional respect to all team members; personal accountability; trustworthiness; and&nbsp;teamwork</li>  </ul>    <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>    <div>  <div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Ernst &amp; Young -&nbsp;Talent Team</strong></div>    <div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Indonesia Stock Exchange Building, Tower I &ndash; 12th floor, Jl. Jend. Sudirman Kav 52-53, Jakarta 12190</strong></div>  </div>  </div> </div>', '<ul class=\"list-unstyled hidden-xs\" id=\"job_desc_detail_4\">  <li>Join Fraud Investigation &amp; Dispute Services within Assurance and you will help clients work through complex issues of fraud, regulatory compliance...</li>																													</ul>', '<div class=\"panel panel-clean\"> 				<div class=\"panel-body position_panel\"> 				    					<div class=\"col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-3 col-xs-12\">						 						<div class=\"logo_sm_wrap\"> 							<img id=\"company_logo\" alt=\"Fraud Investigation and Dispute Services Consultant - PT Ernst & Young Indonesia - Logo\" 								data-original=\"https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/6397/images/sol/6397_logo_0_6060017.jpg\"> 						</div>						 					</div> 					<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-5 col-xs-12\">					    										   <div class=\"job-position-wrap\">						         						<h1 id=\"position_title\" class=\"job-position\">Fraud Investigation and Dispute Services Consultant</h1>     						<div id=\"company_name\" class=\"company_name\">     							    							        							        <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.jobstreet.co.id/en/companies/717198-pt-ernst-n-young-indonesia\">PT Ernst & Young In