(161, 'IT Programmer Supervisor-PT Morula Indonesia ', '<div class=\"unselectable wrap-text\" id=\"job_description\"> <div>Job Requirements :</div>    <ul>  	<li>Min. Bachelor degree from IT</li>  	<li>Age from 25-30 years old.</li>  	<li><strong>Experience in 4 years (Preferably from Health / Clinic / Hospital preferred)</strong></li>  	<li><strong>Skill Programming PHP Moderate - Advance (Code Igniter - JSON - API)</strong></li>  	<li><strong>Skill SQL Server dan MySql Moederate - Advance</strong></li>  	<li>at least working on 2 sofware projects</li>  	<li>Training enduser</li>  	<li>Willing to travel around Indonesia</li>  </ul>    <div>If you&rsquo;re interested, please kindly send us your profile to recruitment at morulaivf dot co dot id and puspita.hapsari at morulaivf dot co dot id</div>    <div><br />  Have a great day.</div> </div>', '<ul class=\"list-unstyled hidden-xs\" id=\"job_desc_detail_6\">  <li>Job Requirements : Min. Bachelor degree from IT. Age from 25-30 years old. Experience in 4 years (Preferably from Health / Clinic / Hospital...</li>																													</ul>', '<div class=\"panel panel-clean\"> 				<div class=\"panel-body position_panel\"> 				    					<div class=\"col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-3 col-xs-12\">						 						<div class=\"logo_sm_wrap\"> 							<img id=\"company_logo\" alt=\"IT Programmer Supervisor - PT Morula Indonesia - Logo\" 								data-original=\"https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/59469/images/sol/59469_logo_0_920459.jpg\"> 						</div>						 					</div> 					<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-5 col-xs-12\">					    										   <div class=\"job-position-wrap\">						         						<h1 id=\"position_title\" class=\"job-position\">IT Programmer Supervisor</h1>     						<div id=\"company_name\" class=\"company_name\">     							    							        							        <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.jobstreet.co.id/en/companies/832718-pt-morula-indonesia\">PT Morula Indonesia</a>     							      																					</div> 												   </div> 					</div> 					<div class=\"col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 table-location-div\"> 					    <div class=\"job-info-wrap\">     						                            <div id=\"salary\" class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-sx-12\"></div>     						<div id=\"experience\" class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-sx-12\">     							<p id=\"years_of_experience\" class=\"main_desc_detail\"> 	<span class=\"main_desc_icon\"> 		<span class=\"icon-briefcase icon_left experience\"></span> 	</span> 	<span id=\"years_of_experience\"> 			Min 3 tahun (Supervisor/Koordinator)  		</span> </p> 				 </div>                                 						<div id=\"location\" class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-sx-12\">     							<p class=\"main_desc_detail\" > 	<span id=\"work_location\" class=\"main_desc_icon\"> 		<span class=\"icon-location icon_left location\"></span> 	</span> 			<span id=\"single_work_location\" class=\"single_work_location\"> 			Indonesia - Jakarta Raya - Jakarta Pusat - Menteng		</span> 	</p> 			 			 			</div>     					</div> 					</div> 				</div> 			</div>', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"> 								<p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"><div> <div> <div style=\"text-align:justify\">Morula IVF is the biggest IVF center in Indonesia which was established in 1998.</div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\">It is the first and the only clinic in Indonesia which had achieved International Certification Reproductive Technology Accreditation Committee (RTAC) from The Joint Accreditation System of Australia and New Zealand (JAS - ANZ).</div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\">Nowadays Morula IVF is growing rapidly and already has several branches, such as: Morula IVF Margonda (Depok), Morula IVF Padang, Morula IVF Surabaya, Morula IVF Melinda Bandung, Morula IVF Pontianak and Morula IVF Makassar. In the next 3-4 years, Morula IVF plans to go public.</div> </div> </div>  <div>&nbsp;</div></p> 	