n Japan, to provide new opportunities to our clients across the region.</div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">RGF HR AGENT takes charge of RGF&rsquo;s business entity in general recruitment services. We provide total human resource services to clients at every stage of staff placement, such as evaluation, remuneration, and staff training. At the same time, we assist job-seekers in various ways to find the right job according to their individual preferences and experiences. Besides our services to assist full time staff recruitment, we also offer a range of support services for RPO (Recruitment Process Outsourcing) and contract base/temporary recruitment needs.</div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Our Company&rsquo;s status as the Japan #1 market share holder in human resource, temporary staffing, and job advertisement field makes it possible for us to provide high quality total human resource management services not only in Japan but across the region.</div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">We just open our RGF HR AGENT Brand in Indonesia on 1st May, 2013 and will continue and expand the business for the future.</div></div><div>&nbsp;</div></p> 							</div>', '', '<img class=\"img-company-logo\" id=\"img_company_logo_9\" src=\"https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/40909/images/logo/40909_logo_0_393009.jpeg\" alt=\"Lowongan RGF HR Agent Indonesia\">', 'Penjualan Ritel', ' &#62; Akuntansi &amp; Laporan Keuangan', 'Retail / Merchandise ', 'Jakarta Raya ', 'RGF HR Agent Indonesia ', 'Ditayangkan: 16-October-2019 ', ' 							  							  Tutup pada 15-November-2019', '2019-11-15', '2019-10-16', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/tax-import-control-staff-3097817?fr=J&searchRequestToken=04176d0c-773c-47fe-ee37-a0e10044bfaa&sectionRank=9', 'Graha Pratama, P1(21st) Floor, Jl. M.T.Haryono Kav. 15, Jakarta 12810, Indonesia', 'Tax-&amp;