ia ', 'Ditayangkan: 18-October-2019 ', ' 							  							  Tutup pada 17-November-2019', '2019-11-17', '2019-10-18', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/route-sales-3100740?fr=J&searchRequestToken=ecd1aff2-d3d2-46d5-8270-322fcfa52e08&sectionRank=4', 'Wisma KEIAI lt.18 jln. Jenderal Sudirman kav 3-4 jakarta 10220', 'Route-Sales', 'yogyakarta', 'active'),
