overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"><div style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>PT. Marton Tekindo Abadi</strong> is a private company that is growing rapidly, engaged in the mining and construction equipment . As an authorized distributor of original stone crusher Shanbao, Junjin drilling machines, and variety of other well-known products .</div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>PT. Marton Tekindo Abadi</strong> adalah perusahaan swasta yang sedang berkembang pesat, bergerak di bidang peralatan tambang dan konstruksi. Sebagai distributor resmi stone crusher original Shanbao, mesin bor Junjin, dan berbagai produk ternama lainnya.</div></p> 							</div>', '<p id=\"why_join_us\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"><div>Kami menawarkan peluang kerja dan kesempatan berkarir yang sama untuk semua level jabatan, suasana kerja yang kondusif dan transparan, serta target kerja yang membuat Anda bisa memberikan kemampuan maksimal bagi perkembangan perusahaan. Kami juga memberikan kesempatan bagi setiap karyawan untuk meningkatkan kapasitas pribadinya sehingga mampu menjadi pengelola dan pemilik dari sebuah unit usaha secara mandiri.</div></p>', '<img class=\"img-company-logo\" id=\"img_company_logo_3\" src=\"https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/46945/images/logo/46945_logo_0_7855768.jpg\" alt=\"Lowongan PT. Marton Tekindo Abadi\">', 'Teknik Lainnya', ' &#62; Akuntansi &amp; Laporan Keuangan', 'Manufaktur / Produksi ', 'Jakarta Utara (Jakarta Raya) ', 'PT. Marton Tekindo Abadi ', 'Ditayangkan: 19-October-2019 ', ' 							  							  Tutup pada 18-November-2019', '2019-11-18', '2019-10-19', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/sales-engineer-3100599?fr=J&searchRequestToken=d999e687-a8ff-490e-eb24-d212c8e02fd5&sectionRank=3', 'Kelapa Gading Boulevard Blok PA 11/15, East Kelapa Gading, Jakarta, Indonesia', 'Sales-Engineer', 'jabodetabek', 'active'),
(204, 'Marketing Executive-PT Citra Bhakti Sejahtera ', '<div class=\"unselectable wrap-text\" id=\"job_description\"> <div>  <div><strong>Requirement and Qualifications :</strong></div>    <ul>  	<li>S1 degree, Faculty of Transportation and Logistics</li>  	<li>Communication skills in English</li>  	<li>Minimal 2 years experience in marketing and sales in Logistics, Freight Forwarding and Transportation Reliable and Responsible</li>  </ul>    <div>&nbsp;</div>    <div><strong>Tasks and Responsibilities :</strong></div>    <div>&nbsp;</div>    <ul>  	<li>Collect database of potential customers</li>  	<li>Visit and do the presentation about the information of our services to customers</li>  	<li>Obtain the shipment from potential customers</li>  	<li>Maintain business relationship with existing customers either by phone or visit</li>  	<li>Prepare the reporting periodically</li>  </ul>    <div>&nbsp;</div>  </div> </div>', '<ul class=\"list-unstyled hidden-xs\" id=\"job_desc_detail_4\">  <li>Requirement and Qualifications : S1 degree, Faculty of Transportation and Logistics. Communication skills in English. Minimal 2 years experience in...</li>																													</ul>', '<div class=\"panel panel-clean\"> 				<div class=\"panel-body position_panel\"> 				    					<div class=\"col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-3 col-xs-12\">						 						<div class=\"logo_sm_wrap\"> 							<img id=\"company_logo\" alt=\"Marketing Executive - PT Citra Bhakti Sejahtera - Logo\" 								data-original=\"https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/157476/images/sol/157476_logo_0_678554.jpg\"> 						</div>						 					</div> 					<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-5 col-xs-12\">					    										   <div class=\"job-position-wrap\">						         						<h1 id=\"position_title\" class=\"job-position\">Marketing Executive</h1>     						<div id=\"company_name\" class=\"company_name\">     							    							        							        <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.jobstreet.co.id/en/companies/1243385-pt-citra-bhakti-sejahtera\">PT Citra Bhakti Sejahtera</a>     							      																					</div> 												   </div> 					</div> 					<div class=\"col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 table-location-div\"> 					    <div class=\"job-info-wrap\">     						                            <div id=\"salary\" class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-sx-12\"></div>     						<div id=\"experience\" class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-sx-12\">     							<p id=\"years_of_experience\" class=\"main_desc_detail\"> 	<span class=\"main_desc_icon\"> 		<span class=\"icon-briefcase icon_left experience\"></span> 	</span> 	<span id=\"years_of_experience\"> 			Min 2 tahun (Pegawai (non-manajemen & non-supervisor))  		</span> </p> 				 </div>                                 						<div id=\"location\" class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-sx-12\">     							<p class=\"main_desc_detail\" > 	<span id=\"work_location\" class=\"main_desc_icon\"> 		<span class=\"icon-location icon_left location\"></span> 	</span> 			<span id=\"single_work_location\" class=\"single_work_location\"> 			Indonesia - Jakarta Raya		</span> 	</p> 			 			 			</div>     					</div> 					</div> 				</div> 			</div>', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"> 								<p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"><div> <div style=\"text-align:justify\">PT. Citra Bhakti Sejahtera as part of the CBS Group was established in 2006, consisting of companies conducting business related to Business Process and Import Process. Our company dealing business in Legal, Logistic, Customs Services and Customs Consultant</div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\">We do joint operation with <strong>Mach 1</strong> as International forwarder which is the head office in USA and also many network branches in the world.</div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\">We provide :</div>  <ol> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">Legal &amp; Customs Consultant</li> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">Customs Services</li> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">Logistics &amp; Project</li> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">Handling Freight</li> </ol>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\">In our business course, as a member of Indonesia Customs Services Association , &nbsp;Asosiasi Pengusaha Pengurusan Jasa &nbsp;Kepabeanan &nbsp;Indonesia and as Chief of Board Jakarta, we often writes opinion or comment about customs in daily newspaper Bisnis Indonesia, and participate in meetings and seminars held by ASAKINDO or others to increase our knowledge of customs services and forwarding, and also socialization with other members and the development of the applicable law and regulation in customs.</div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\">We are also member active to attend regular members gathering and CEO/owner gathering with Government Officer and Ministry to talk about variant economic issue like regulation, government policy, etc.</div> </div></p> 							</div>', '', '<img class=\"img-company-logo\" id=\"img_company_logo_4\" src=\"https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/157476/images/logo/157476_logo_0_678554.jpg\" alt=\"Lowongan PT Citra Bhakti Sejahtera\">', 'Teknik Lainnya', ' &#62; Akuntansi &amp; Laporan Keuangan', 'Manufaktur / Produksi ', 'Jakarta Raya ', 'PT Citra Bhakti Sejahtera ', 'Ditayangkan: 19-October-2019 ', ' 							  							  Tutup pada 18-November-2019', '2019-11-18', '2019-10-19', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/marketing-executive-3100131?fr=J&searchRequestToken=d999e687-a8ff-490e-eb24-d212c8e02fd5&sectionRank=4', '', 'Marketing-Executive', 'jabodetabek', 'active');
